CatDescriptText: Cutline of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 4, 1954, pg. 1 reads: "200 Babies Vie For Cash Prizes - Results of Carnation's first annual Hometown "Healthy Baby Contest" were announced last Saturday morning at a special gathering held in All Purpose Room of the Centre Avenue YMCA..."
TitMainTitle: Double exposure of two group portraits of babies, men, and women, including one second from left wearing a diamond patterned plaid top, gathered behind table in Centre Avenue YMCA for Carnation Milk baby contest
